I0. Notes on vetting the gathered explanations

    argument
        - none of the soley physics/nature-based explanations satisfies
            ∵ each leaves a residue of unexplained surprise at reality being so structured that hardly
              could a viable, life-supporting cosmos exist unless (surprise!) it also afforded
              a long-term safehold for mind
                ∵ one then wonders at such open questions as: what constraint on reality
                  so slims the possibilities?  whence comes it, and why?
                / thus the residue of surprise and the call for a more satisfying explanation
        - (a variant of) the design hypothesis can do better in this regard
            ∵ easily the mind of a designer can explain the presence of the safehold
            ∵ especially, deeply satisfying: the existence of the original designer can then, in turn,
              easily be explained by the (soley physics/nature-based) multiverse ensemble hypothesis
                ∵ given a numerous and diverse enough ensemble of cosmoi, it should be no surprise that
                  one of the number happens (its structure sufficing) to evolve a line of noons|cogitants
                  who manage to survive there long enough to figure out how (speculating it is possible)
                  to sustain the multiverse game lineally, in time, as a line of [successive] cosmoi
                    - together these noons|cogitants are the original cosmic designer/creator
                    - they make a new cosmos (or multiple cosmoi, each) complete with a safehold
                      whose (eventual) occupants they intend will:
                        a) become cosmic designers themselves,
                        b) repeat the performance, and
                        c) keep the newly created line of cosmoi going indefinitely
    feasiblity?  what are my prospects for refuting P?  what for asserting Q?

            P: Hardly could we living noons|cogitants be here absent the cosmic speed limit on causation.
            Q: Easily could we living noons|cogitants be here absent the cosmic speed limit on causation.

            if( P ) then
                - design might suffice (to explain the safehold)
                - known rivals (OS, ME) might suffice
            else if( Q ) then
                - design might suffice
                † known rivals (OS, ME) would not suffice
            else
                - unsure, maybe a toss up

        ⇒ promising
